Write a script to list methods of a package/class.

## Example

    package Calc;

    use strict;
    use warnings;

    sub new { bless {}, shift; }
    sub add { }
    sub mul { }
    sub div { }

    1;

## Output

    BEGIN
    mul
    div
    new
    add

